{"title":"烈火炼英雄","authors":["吴洪源"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":9,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火炼英雄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部　吴洪源"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的钻井队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是好呀真是好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一座大熔炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是一所大学校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想学到手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人敢把重担挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响应领袖号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏上革命大道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找气找油为祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"餐风宿露不辞劳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的钻井队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋战大油田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井架高高竖起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻机隆隆震山川；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手捉住气老虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心开发大油田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜艰苦奋战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干劲冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最高指示牢记心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海只等闲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的钻井队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人肝胆红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气井爆炸起大火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个勇猛向前冲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐心合力去抢救，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕它烈焰逞凶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚守战斗岗位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家财富记心中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏平火海千层浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火当中炼英雄！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}